<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 06:09:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>居民告诉以色列-加沙边境附近重建基布兹尼尔奥兹需要两年时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/rebuilding-kibbutz-nir-oz-near-the-israeli-gaza-border-will-take-two-years-residents-told/0000018b-6853-d979-a3bb-eb779ae50000</link><description>基布兹居民将在以色列各地找到临时住房，并决定社区的下一步发展。有些家庭根本不确定他们是否会回来</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 05:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/rebuilding-kibbutz-nir-oz-near-the-israeli-gaza-border-will-take-two-years-residents-told/0000018b-6853-d979-a3bb-eb779ae50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙发动夜间地面攻势，称袭击哈马斯成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-live/.premium/idf-intercepts-rocket-shot-from-lebanon-putin-conflict-may-spill-over-beyond-middle-east/0000018b-69d2-d979-a3bb-ebf7c9c20000</link><description>以色列国防军连夜拦截了一枚来自黎巴嫩的地对空导弹，以色列空军瞄准了发射源。来自加沙的火箭袭击了以色列中部的住宅楼 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少造成 1,300 人死亡 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：超过 6,000 名加沙人死亡，约 17,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 04:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article-live/.premium/idf-intercepts-rocket-shot-from-lebanon-putin-conflict-may-spill-over-beyond-middle-east/0000018b-69d2-d979-a3bb-ebf7c9c20000</guid></item><item><title>随着人质的时间流逝，以色列依赖哈马斯盟友卡塔尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/as-clock-ticks-for-hostages-israel-dependent-on-hamas-ally-qatar/0000018b-6886-db57-a7cb-e89fc4e00000</link><description>卡塔尔的谈判重点是让被扣为人质的妇女、儿童和老人回家，以及向加沙引入燃料。随着战争的继续，以色列接下来将面临加沙地下隧道和北部日益紧张的局势的挑战</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 03:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/as-clock-ticks-for-hostages-israel-dependent-on-hamas-ally-qatar/0000018b-6886-db57-a7cb-e89fc4e00000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚上空的间谍卫星揭示了数百座古罗马堡垒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/spy-satellites-over-syria-reveal-hundreds-of-ancient-roman-forts/0000018b-624e-d288-afef-f2deff9e0000</link><description>20 年代，一位耶稣会考古学家飞越近东地区寻找罗马堡垒，并最终找到了它们。新解密的冷战图像显示了数百张图像，也表明波德巴德神父的解释完全错误</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 03:08:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-26/ty-article-magazine/spy-satellites-over-syria-reveal-hundreds-of-ancient-roman-forts/0000018b-624e-d288-afef-f2deff9e0000</guid></item><item><title>释放加沙“许多”以色列人质和外国人质的谈判正在进行中；可能在“几天内”发布</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/sources-many-hostages-could-be-released-within-days/0000018b-6881-d78a-a5eb-7c8383710000</link><description>以色列正在推进一项单方面释放所有被俘公民的计划，但参与与哈马斯谈判的消息人士发现，很难估计其中有多少人将被释放以及在什么条件下被释放</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 02:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/sources-many-hostages-could-be-released-within-days/0000018b-6881-d78a-a5eb-7c8383710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公民仅仅因为是阿拉伯人就遭到咒骂、威胁、解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-citizens-cursed-threatened-fired-from-their-jobs-simply-for-being-arab/0000018b-6884-d979-a3bb-ebf7eee40000</link><description>战争爆发以来，许多以色列阿拉伯人不敢离开家园。他们讲述了犹太城市的袭击、谋杀威胁、羞辱和种族主义诽谤，以及终止或暂停就业的情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 00:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-citizens-cursed-threatened-fired-from-their-jobs-simply-for-being-arab/0000018b-6884-d979-a3bb-ebf7eee40000</guid></item><item><title>不惜一切代价带回以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/bring-back-the-israeli-hostages-at-any-price/0000018b-6814-d326-a39b-6e1ca6630000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 22:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article/.premium/bring-back-the-israeli-hostages-at-any-price/0000018b-6814-d326-a39b-6e1ca6630000</guid></item><item><title>黑暗笼罩在以色列的脸上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/and-darkness-was-upon-the-face-of-israel/0000018b-6813-d78a-a5eb-7c93d6fe0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 21:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/and-darkness-was-upon-the-face-of-israel/0000018b-6813-d78a-a5eb-7c93d6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>用他自己的话说：这就是内塔尼亚胡必须下台的原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-his-own-words-this-is-why-netanyahu-must-go/0000018b-6814-d78a-a5eb-7c9729f30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 20:43:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-his-own-words-this-is-why-netanyahu-must-go/0000018b-6814-d78a-a5eb-7c9729f30000</guid></item><item><title>大屠杀基金会将收集并保存 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击以色列幸存者的证词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/shoah-foundation-to-collect-testimonies-from-survivors-of-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-681b-d979-a3bb-eb7f681f0000</link><description>该基金会的工作团队已积累了超过 56,000 个世界各地种族灭绝、反人类罪和相关迫害幸存者的视频证词，并已在以色列录制了第一批证词</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 19:45:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/shoah-foundation-to-collect-testimonies-from-survivors-of-oct-7-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-681b-d979-a3bb-eb7f681f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登称两国解决方案必须在以色列与哈马斯战争之后实施，并抨击“极端主义”西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-two-state-solution-must-follow-israel-hamas-war-slams-extremist-settlers/0000018b-6838-d78a-a5eb-7cbb32020000</link><description>在迄今为止对战争最广泛的评论中，美国总统还质疑哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部的伤亡数字，并敦促继续与沙特阿拉伯进行谈判</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 19:33:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-two-state-solution-must-follow-israel-hamas-war-slams-extremist-settlers/0000018b-6838-d78a-a5eb-7cbb32020000</guid></item><item><title>新众议院议长迈克·约翰逊是一位福音派基督徒，与以色列极右翼分子有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/new-house-speaker-mike-johnson-an-evangelical-christian-holds-ties-to-israels-far-right/0000018b-67b3-db57-a7cb-efbf8a8d0000</link><description>路易斯安那州众议员迈克·约翰逊 (Mike Johnson) 将他 2020 年对耶路撒冷圣殿山的访问描述为“圣经预言的实现”；他的当选是华盛顿福音派迄今为止最重大的胜利</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/new-house-speaker-mike-johnson-an-evangelical-christian-holds-ties-to-israels-far-right/0000018b-67b3-db57-a7cb-efbf8a8d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称，哈马斯一半以上人质拥有外国公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/more-than-half-of-hamas-hostages-have-foreign-citizenship-israel-says/0000018b-67be-d78a-a5eb-7fbf08360000</link><description>以色列政府称，138名人质持有外国护照，其中包括15名阿根廷人、12名德国人、12名美国人、6名法国人和6名俄罗斯人</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/more-than-half-of-hamas-hostages-have-foreign-citizenship-israel-says/0000018b-67be-d78a-a5eb-7fbf08360000</guid></item><item><title>“我们现在都需要治疗”：特拉维夫画廊为战争提供喘息空间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-all-need-therapy-now-the-tel-aviv-gallery-offering-breathing-space-from-the-war/0000018b-6722-d979-a3bb-ef77d3650000</link><description>“菌丝体”是一个与众不同的装置：部分是艺术体验，部分是治疗诊所——它的时机再合适不过了。艺术家莎朗·格拉兹伯格 (Sharon Glazberg) 表示，“这个空间仿佛就是为此而生”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:40:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-all-need-therapy-now-the-tel-aviv-gallery-offering-breathing-space-from-the-war/0000018b-6722-d979-a3bb-ef77d3650000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列推迟入侵加沙，以便美国加强中东地区的防御</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-gaza-invasion-so-u-s-can-bolster-defenses-across-mideast-wsj-reports/0000018b-6783-d326-a39b-679bc63f0000</link><description>报道称，以色列将推迟行动，直到美国加强中东地区的防御。然而，美国官员进一步担心人质谈判和人道主义危机的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 17:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-delaying-gaza-invasion-so-u-s-can-bolster-defenses-across-mideast-wsj-reports/0000018b-6783-d326-a39b-679bc63f0000</guid></item><item><title>捷克和奥地利领导人访问以色列承诺声援哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/visiting-israel-leaders-of-czech-republic-austria-pledge-solidarity-against-hamas/0000018b-6763-d979-a3bb-ef77992a0000</link><description>捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉称哈马斯为“共同的敌人”，奥地利总理卡尔·内哈默在与以色列总理和总统的会晤中谈到“共同打击恐怖主义”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 16:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/visiting-israel-leaders-of-czech-republic-austria-pledge-solidarity-against-hamas/0000018b-6763-d979-a3bb-ef77992a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯正在考验以色列的“特氟龙经济”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-putting-israels-teflon-economy-to-the-test/0000018b-675d-d979-a3bb-ef7f51e50000</link><description>标准普尔、穆迪和惠誉尚未准备好降低以色列的信用评级，但战争才刚刚开始。如果他们这样做的话会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 15:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/hamas-is-putting-israels-teflon-economy-to-the-test/0000018b-675d-d979-a3bb-ef7f51e50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯袭击后以色列境外犹太人的恐惧和创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-fear-and-trauma-of-jews-outside-israel-after-the-hamas-attacks/0000018b-66be-db57-a7cb-eebf2e530000</link><description>今天，作为一名在伦敦的犹太人，我感受到了以前从未经历过的恐惧。世界各地的犹太社区正在努力应对 10 月 7 日的创伤以及对当天野蛮行径的可悲反应</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 14:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-25/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-fear-and-trauma-of-jews-outside-israel-after-the-hamas-attacks/0000018b-66be-db57-a7cb-eebf2e530000</guid></item><item><title>约旦女王声称媒体和国际社会对以色列和巴勒斯坦死亡问题采取“双重标准”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/jordans-queen-claims-double-standard-regarding-israeli-palestinian-deaths/0000018b-66d8-d1c5-af9f-77fb74c20000</link><description>在接受美国有线电视新闻网采访时，约旦女王拉尼娅谴责西方对加沙的偏见，称有关“以色列儿童在基布兹被屠杀”的报道未经证实</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 13:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/jordans-queen-claims-double-standard-regarding-israeli-palestinian-deaths/0000018b-66d8-d1c5-af9f-77fb74c20000</guid></item><item><title>美国各地校园计划举行罢工抗议“加沙种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/walkouts-protesting-gaza-genocide-planned-on-campuses-across-u-s/0000018b-66b9-d326-a39b-66b9b8130000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件以来，美国校园的紧张局势已升级至前所未有的水平，该事件造成 1,400 名以色列人死亡、220 人被囚禁，而在以色列对袭击作出反应后，加沙有超过 6,500 名巴勒斯坦人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 12:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-25/ty-article/.premium/walkouts-protesting-gaza-genocide-planned-on-campuses-across-u-s/0000018b-66b9-d326-a39b-66b9b8130000</guid></item></channel></rss>